title: Donovan Mitchell Destination Rankings, Plus Rob’s First Mailbag | Group Chat
description:
Justin and Rob start by ranking their favorite possible trade destinations for Donovan Mitchell (5:05). Then they answer a bunch of listener questions, including questions about the Thunder, summer league memories, Collin Sexton, and more (44:22).

Hosts: Justin Verrier and Rob Mahoney
Associate Producer: Isaiah Blakely
